    "_dioramaComment": "Coordinate convention: +Z = south, -Z = north, +X = east, -X = west. Basecamp safe zone spans x[-10..10] z[-10..10]. Market zone sits just outside the NORTH edge (z=-8 to z=-20). Factory sits just outside the WEST gate (x<-10). Jungle/Nature sprawls across the entire east side. Mountains form a far backdrop on the NE arc. Hive holds the SW combat frontier. The big razor-wire wall runs full map width along z=14, with a 4-unit central gap for the player to walk through to the combat front.",
