        "_zombieScaleComment": "Uniform multiplier applied to scatter+landmark props with z > zombieAreaZ (i.e. south of the big fence). Set to 1.0 (or remove) to restore original sizes. Affects destroyed houses, cars, tires, barrels, corpses, sandbags, hive, etc. Does NOT affect player, basecamp, restaurant, factory, jungle, pads, mountains, or the fence.",
